          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg">Deirdre V. Lyons </h3>
          
          <p class="text-md">She/Her </p> 
          <p class="text-sm">Deirdre V. Lyons is a LA producer, director, and performer, she is a co-founder of Ferryman Collective, creating live theatre in VR, including the award-winning Welcome to Respite and Gumball Dreams, named Best Experience of 2022 and Creator of the Year by XR Must. She was a 2023 SXSW mentor, included in the 2021 list of Top 100 Original Voices in XR, honored with the 2023 Innovation Award from XR Women and included in V2 of the Global Top 100 Women in Emerging Tech. She is a sought-after speaker and was recently accepted into the Producers Guild of America. </p>
          
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.DeirdreVLyons.com"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Website</a>
            
            
            
