          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg">Natasha Sebben AKA natsha </h3>
          
          <p class="text-md">She/Her </p> 
          <p class="text-sm">Natasha Sebben AKA natsha is a narrative and game designer. She’s currently developing Psychotic Bathtub – a multilinear story game about a psychotic disorder. And ducks. Additionally, natsha works as a teaching assistant at the Zurich University of the Arts and supports studios in the creation of their stories. </p>
          
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://natsha.ch"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Website</a>
            
            
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/natsha_sebben"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Instagram</a>
            
            
          
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-4 pb-5 jury">
          
