          </div>
          

          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg">Shuhei Yoshida </h3>
          
          <p class="text-md">He/Him </p> 
          <p class="text-sm">Shuhei Yoshida has been with the PlayStation since the project&rsquo;s inception more than 30 years ago. As the President of WWS, Yoshida oversaw development of global best-selling franchises, such as God of War®, Horizon Zero Dawn™ and The Last of Us®. In Nov. 2019, Yoshida became Head of Indies Initiative where he helps external independent creators to ensure they have the tools, technology, and services to reach PlayStation’s large community of gamers successfully. </p>
          
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://blog.playstation.com"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Website</a>
            
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.twitter.com/yosp"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Twitter</a>
            
            
            
          
