          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg">Vanessa Amoah Opoku </h3>
          
          <p class="text-md">She/Her </p> 
          <p class="text-sm">Vanessa Amoah Opoku is an interdisciplinary artist who focuses on history, technology, and marginalized narratives within mixed realities. In her artistic practice, she reflects on how alliances between art, science, and technology can change perceptions of our world, reality, and all living things. Her preferred media include 3D graphics, animation, sculpture, photogrammetry, sound, and artificial intelligence. </p>
          
            
            <a target="_blank" href="https://vanessaopoku.com"><i class="tf-ion-android-arrow-forward"></i> Website</a>
            
            
            
